{"tid":1440741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浙江永嘉縣堰塞湖決堤　增至最少18人死亡","createTime":"2019-08-10T13:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T04:10:35.000Z","uid":41404,"like":221,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"3b7798a4e484d96e127b22c446b19ecc7dbd67ea","tid":1440741,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:42:45.000Z","msg":"颱風利奇馬凌晨在浙江溫嶺市登陸，永嘉縣岩坦鎮山早村因特大暴雨，引發山泥傾瀉，形成堰塞湖並突然決提，死亡人數增至18人，仍有14人失蹤，當局加緊搜救。<br />\n<br />\n浙江全省有超過300萬人受災，200多間房屋倒塌，3000多間房屋受損，多處斷電。<br />\n<br />\n利奇馬已減弱為強烈熱帶風暴，上海疏散洋山港、長江上海段1000多艘船隻，郵輪推遲進港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473864-20190810.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473864-20190810.htm&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPFKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=e9c84849\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473864-20190810.htm&h=9db18dc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473864-20190810.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9b60ae3a15d4ad707861b313dc1d374d63a9a40b","tid":1440741,"uid":221265,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:43:15.000Z","msg":"咁少？"},{"pid":"4f8628ca5e5c53255d839424810e3ec357e3b179","tid":1440741,"uid":61032,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />熱烈地彈琴熱烈地唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2bd5ca8b5f74865668d5c7d0a22a42d5dde65a","tid":1440741,"uid":176166,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:43:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36e43e13e6a7f5870b09